word_mean_info__list.difference: 指得出结论，达成某项协议或作出某一决定等。
侧重指在抱负或雄心的激励下，以最大的努力去达到一般所不及或不敢追求的目的。
常用词，指到达某一空间、时间、目标或发展过程中的某一点。
侧重为达到目的所需的技巧、忍耐和努力。
为正式用词，多用于庄重场合，主要指通过努力达到重要目的或得到珍贵的东西。如：The scientist attained great fame by a new discovery.(那科学家由于一次新发现而出了名。)
指通过本身的努力逐渐获得知识、能力和荣誉等。如：acquire knowledge(获得知识)。
多指凭努力或恳求得到急需或很想得到的东西。如：Howard had failed to obtain a scholarship.(霍华德没能得到奖学金。)
用得最广，可指以各种方式获得各种东西。如：Where can I get enough information?(我从哪儿能得到足够的资料？)
多指克服困难后取得胜利，成功，强调“得到”这一结果。如：He achieved his ambition in the end.(他最终实现了他的抱负。)
多指付出极大努力后获得或赢得给自己带来优势的东西。如：They gained the victory after a bloody battle.(浴血奋战后他们赢得了胜利。)

bilingual.source: It made me feel like I could achieve anything.
bilingual.target: 这让我觉得我可以实现任何事情。

bilingual.source: Of course we want to see him achieve his dreams.
bilingual.target: 当然我们希望看到他实现梦想。

bilingual.source: Only then will I have a chance to achieve my dream.
bilingual.target: 只有这样我才有机会实现我的梦想。

bilingual.source: Think about the things you want to achieve at high school.
bilingual.target: 想想你在高中想要实现的事情。

bilingual.source: These stars encourage young people to work hard to achieve their dreams.
bilingual.target: 这些明星鼓励年轻人努力实现他们的梦想。
他为了实现梦想而努力争取。

bilingual.source: One day, I will achieve my dreams.
bilingual.target: 一天，我会实现我的梦想。

bilingual.source: She worked hard to achieve her goal.
bilingual.target: 她通过努力工作实现目标。

bilingual.source: We worked together to achieve our goal.
bilingual.target: 我们一起努力实现目标。

bilingual.source: He works hard to achieve his target.
bilingual.target: 他努力工作以实现他的目标。

list.abstract: achieve（英[əˈtʃiːv]，美[əˈtʃiːv]），英语单词，动词，意思为达到；取得；获得。短语搭配有achieve one's dream（实现某人梦想），例句为“It helps to achieve immersive reading.（这有助于实现沉浸式阅读。）” achieve及物动词类近义词有accomplish、carry out、perform等，不及物动词类近义词有gain one's ends、Make it，名词形式为achievement，形容词形式为achievable。achieved为achieve的过去式以及过去分词形式。

yingyinNormal.en: What I mean is that, to me, hyper-realism is the best way to choose one's dreams and then achieve them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对我来说，非常现实的态度是选择和实现个人梦想。

yingyinNormal.en: My focus is to remain doing my job, which is to ensure prosperity for the American people, and to try to achieve...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的关注点是做好我的工作，也就是确保美国人民繁荣富强，并努力实现...

yingyinNormal.en: Each of us chooses goals based on our values and decides on the best path to achieve them. But we all need approaches to making decisions that work well, especially when facing problems, mistakes, and weaknesses that stand in our way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人的目标都基于自己的价值观实现目标最佳的方法要自己去决定。但我们需要一个良好的决策方法特别是面对问题、错误和弱点阻碍我们前进的时候。

yingyinNormal.en: What would that achieve? I admire that, Frank.
yingyinNormal.zh: 生气有什么好处？我很钦佩，弗兰克。

yingyinNormal.en: In one day, you've managed to do what it takes many couples decades to achieve.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你只用了短短一天就达到许多夫妻花了几十年才达到的境界。

yingyinNormal.en: And you don't think I can achieve the required intimacy via text messaging? Probably not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得通过短信息我无法达到必要的亲密吗？应该不能。

yingyinNormal.en: Pregnant? That's right. All right, now, what are the two ways that you can achieve that goal?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怀孕？正确，好了，现在有两个办法可以避免你怀孕，你知道是什么吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Paper towel users, on the other hand, could achieve more than 85% dryness with only 5 seconds.
yingyinNormal.zh: 另一方面，使用纸巾的人，5秒内就可以去除百分之八十五的湿气。

yingyinNormal.en: Humans didn't create them, but we can use them to foster our own evolution and achieve our goals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法则不是人类创造，但我们可以利用法则培养进步，达到目标。

yingyinNormal.en: I understand what the president hoped to achieve, but the thought of provoking Russia. And I'm just beginning to immerse myself in all the complexities.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我理解总统希望达到什么，但一想到激怒俄国……我这才刚开始了解此事的复杂性。

yingyinNormal.en: The average air dryer requires nearly 45 seconds to reduce hand moisture by 97%, whereas paper towel users achieve the same thing in around only 10 seconds.
yingyinNormal.zh: 平均下来，烘手机需要45秒才可去除手上百分之九十七的湿气，而纸巾只要在十秒内也能达到同样效果。

yingyinNormal.en: And action. If I achieve my goal, specifically, a new pair of quality pants，then I promise I will give back to the community, wearing said pants. All I need is $1,500.
yingyinNormal.zh: 开始，如果我达到目的，具体来说 就是买到一条新的高档裤子，那我保证我会穿着那条裤子回报社会，我只需要一千五。

yingyinNormal.en: Step one is to know your goals and run after them. What is best for you depends on your nature, so you need to really understand yourself and know what you want to achieve in life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一步知道自己的目标追寻目标。你的天性决定了最适合你的方式，所以你要做的只是理解自己明白想在生活中达成什么。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't tell you which path in life is best for you, because I don't know how important it is for you to achieve big goals relative to how important it is for you to avoid the pains required to get them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我无法说出生活中哪条路最适合你，因为我不知道对于你相对于达成目标中避免辛苦，达成重大目标有多重要。

yingyinNormal.en: That I should be telling other people what to do sounds kind of presumptuous to me, but I'm going to do it, because I believe that the principles that have made me successful could help others achieve their own goals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我觉得自己教育他人怎么做很有点妄自尊大，但我还是要这么做，因为我相信我的成功法则可以帮助他人达到自己的目标。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: This one may be a bit more difficult to pull off, but it can go a long way to <highlight>achieving</highlight> results.

examination_example.sentence_trans: 他在生活中所取得的一切都是来之不易的，他在文学领域的成功也不例外。

examination_example.sentence: When you are struggling to <highlight>achieve</highlight> something important you should believe in yourself and be sure that your decision is the best.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你在努力实现一些重要的事情时，你应该相信自己，并确信你的决定是最好的。
